WEBVTT

01:37.850 --> 01:41.000
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.070 --> 01:43.979
[Episode 29]

01:47.229 --> 01:49.289
My son's hearing aid is custom-made.

01:49.789 --> 01:51.640
You just say you
could not find it and that is it?

01:51.640 --> 01:52.580
What am I supposed to do?

01:52.580 --> 01:53.759
For tomorrow's
foreign language listening test,

01:53.759 --> 01:54.590
what is my son going to do?

01:54.590 --> 01:56.120
Ma'am, please calm down first.

01:56.120 --> 01:57.580
What is the point of giving me water?

01:57.580 --> 01:59.580
What I want is my son's hearing aid.

02:00.150 --> 02:01.620
Ma'am, please calm down.

02:02.230 --> 02:04.630
I will help you solve
any problems you have.

02:07.260 --> 02:07.830
Hello.

02:08.630 --> 02:09.310
Do you remember

02:09.310 --> 02:11.850
when the last time
you took off your hearing aid was?

02:11.850 --> 02:13.400
Why are you questioning him?

02:13.400 --> 02:14.950
He's just a child.
He doesn't remember a thing!

02:14.950 --> 02:16.400
If you twist him with a few words,

02:16.400 --> 02:17.910
it'll be easier for you
to deny it later, right?

02:17.910 --> 02:18.870
I'm telling you,

02:18.960 --> 02:21.220
the hearing aid was lost
in your hotel room.

02:21.220 --> 02:21.910
That forewoman of yours

02:21.910 --> 02:23.470
can't escape responsibility!

02:23.470 --> 02:24.829
Ma'am, please don't worry.

02:24.829 --> 02:26.280
I will go to the executive floor right now

02:26.280 --> 02:27.520
to look into the situation.

02:27.520 --> 02:29.030
Please wait here for a moment.

02:29.030 --> 02:30.190
I'll be right back.

02:45.390 --> 02:46.090
Miyu.

02:46.790 --> 02:47.510
Did you find it?

02:47.510 --> 02:48.190
No.

02:48.510 --> 02:50.079
I searched the room,

02:50.110 --> 02:52.030
checked all the corners in the hallway,

02:52.030 --> 02:53.940
and even took apart the toilet.

02:54.280 --> 02:56.210
Now we are going through the trash,

02:56.240 --> 02:57.770
but still haven't found it.

02:59.430 --> 03:00.700
When did they come back?

03:00.700 --> 03:03.780
I know. The parents came back first,

03:03.870 --> 03:04.920
and then the kid

03:04.940 --> 03:06.540
came back half an hour later.

03:07.280 --> 03:08.110
When the kid came back,

03:08.110 --> 03:09.770
did he have his hearing aid on?

03:10.280 --> 03:11.280
Was he wearing it?

03:11.360 --> 03:12.290
I didn't notice.

03:13.770 --> 03:16.630
The kid must have gone
somewhere else along the way.

03:16.690 --> 03:18.360
You need to clean this up quickly.

03:18.360 --> 03:20.690
The garbage truck is waiting downstairs.

03:20.710 --> 03:22.570
Today is garbage collection day.

03:22.650 --> 03:23.650
What should we do?

03:23.680 --> 03:25.010
What should we do, Miyu?

03:27.120 --> 03:28.840
Ma'am, could you ask the head of logistics

03:28.840 --> 03:29.430
to have

03:29.450 --> 03:30.940
the garbage truck wait a bit longer?

03:30.940 --> 03:31.590
Thank you.

03:31.680 --> 03:32.680
Hurry up.

03:32.910 --> 03:34.190
Okay, thanks.

03:40.430 --> 03:41.740
Mr. Ji is here.

03:43.890 --> 03:45.020
Don't panic.

03:45.480 --> 03:46.740
It's not that serious.

03:54.410 --> 03:56.130
Calm the guests down first.

03:56.560 --> 03:58.020
Leave the rest to me.

03:58.079 --> 03:58.870
Yes, Mr. Ji.

04:02.470 --> 04:04.000
I'll go ask the child again.

04:04.290 --> 04:05.130
Wait for me.

04:06.160 --> 04:06.960
Thanks, Miyu.

04:08.630 --> 04:10.160
-Let’s keep looking.
-Yes.

04:17.760 --> 04:19.550
[Camera 01]

04:20.070 --> 04:20.910
Pause it.

04:24.000 --> 04:25.290
Zoom in on this footage.

04:25.290 --> 04:25.800
Okay.

04:27.850 --> 04:28.830
Focus on the ear.

04:29.240 --> 04:29.800
Yes.

04:36.270 --> 04:37.470
Show me the elevator footage

04:37.470 --> 04:38.490
from that same time.

04:38.490 --> 04:39.090
Yes.

04:46.230 --> 04:47.150
Did you find it?

04:47.170 --> 04:47.830
No.

04:47.860 --> 04:48.680
I wonder whether I can...

04:48.680 --> 04:50.270
Then what are you doing?

04:50.510 --> 04:51.270
You just went up for a stroll,

04:51.270 --> 04:52.560
and came down to say no?

04:52.920 --> 04:54.480
Are you all putting on a show for me?

04:54.480 --> 04:56.250
My son has an exam tomorrow.

04:56.560 --> 04:57.800
The college entrance exam!

04:57.800 --> 04:58.310
Ma'am,

04:58.360 --> 05:00.000
I completely understand how you feel.

05:00.000 --> 05:01.240
That's why I'd like to ask

05:01.240 --> 05:03.190
whether I may speak with your son
alone for a moment.

05:03.190 --> 05:03.720
No.

05:04.350 --> 05:06.300
Please don't rush to speak for him.

05:06.750 --> 05:08.280
Or you can ask him yourself.

05:08.310 --> 05:08.830
Okay?

05:08.870 --> 05:09.720
No.

05:09.750 --> 05:10.830
Why not?

05:11.750 --> 05:12.680
You're so annoying.

05:12.680 --> 05:14.940
No wonder Dad doesn't want to talk to you.

05:29.150 --> 05:30.750
I can answer your questions,

05:30.780 --> 05:32.040
but you must promise me

05:32.190 --> 05:33.280
that you absolutely must not tell

05:33.280 --> 05:35.020
what I tell you to my mom.

05:35.240 --> 05:36.840
Otherwise, she'll go crazy.

05:38.390 --> 05:39.240
I promise.

05:40.370 --> 05:41.170
Go ahead.

05:43.230 --> 05:46.630
[Camera 05]

05:43.950 --> 05:46.310
I had a fight with my mom
in the room yesterday.

05:46.310 --> 05:47.070
I was a bit annoyed,

05:46.640 --> 05:50.190
[Camera 03]

05:47.390 --> 05:49.250
so I wanted to be alone for a while.

05:50.270 --> 05:52.060
Bring up all the footage of this floor.

05:52.060 --> 05:52.659
Okay.

05:55.659 --> 05:57.940
Then I went to the gym by myself.

05:59.870 --> 06:01.240
How long were you there?

06:01.270 --> 06:02.340
What did you do?

06:02.660 --> 06:04.270
I didn't do anything.

06:05.000 --> 06:05.950
I took a nap,

06:06.190 --> 06:07.920
and hurried back
to my room when I woke up.

06:07.920 --> 06:10.050
Did you take off your hearing aid then?

06:10.120 --> 06:11.050
Do you remember?

06:12.750 --> 06:13.780
But after that,

06:13.870 --> 06:15.670
I never saw my hearing aid again.

06:17.630 --> 06:19.000
Recreation Department,
Recreation Department.

06:19.000 --> 06:20.680
Did you find a hearing aid?

06:28.060 --> 06:32.890
[Camera 02]

06:33.360 --> 06:33.800
Okay.

06:34.390 --> 06:35.620
We can speed it up here.

06:35.620 --> 06:36.750
Let's fast forward.

06:39.430 --> 06:41.340
Don't worry, Ma'am.

06:41.560 --> 06:43.430
We should be able to find
your lost item very soon.

06:43.430 --> 06:45.360
Did he go somewhere
to have fun behind my back?

06:45.360 --> 06:46.800
Ms. Xu, tell me,

06:46.930 --> 06:48.170
what did he say to you?

06:49.230 --> 06:49.870
I'm sorry.

06:51.000 --> 06:52.000
I can't tell you.

06:57.530 --> 06:58.390
Why?

07:00.370 --> 07:02.760
Why are all of you avoiding me

07:04.230 --> 07:05.760
and telling me nothing?

07:06.630 --> 07:09.850
I'm always thinking
about what's best for you.

07:11.920 --> 07:14.120
Lu Xiaoyan, do you have tissues?

07:18.680 --> 07:20.800
After the lady calms down,

07:20.870 --> 07:22.240
escort her back to her hotel room to rest.

07:22.240 --> 07:22.680
Got it?

07:22.680 --> 07:23.410
Okay, got it.

07:24.710 --> 07:25.390
Here.

07:26.160 --> 07:26.850
Take this.

07:34.110 --> 07:35.140
Recreation Department,
Recreation Department.

07:35.140 --> 07:36.740
Did you find the hearing aid?

07:41.130 --> 07:43.550
[Camera 02]

07:41.310 --> 07:41.840
Pause it.

07:44.510 --> 07:45.730
Hurry and stop the garbage truck.

07:45.730 --> 07:46.190
Got it.

07:46.210 --> 07:47.460
Also, notify the lobby

07:47.460 --> 07:49.040
and have Ms. Xu calm the guests down.

07:49.040 --> 07:49.570
Yes, Sir.

07:51.060 --> 07:52.460
Hello, is this the lobby?

07:53.950 --> 07:55.920
Ms. Xu, I didn't find the hearing aid.

07:55.920 --> 07:58.040
Ms. Xu, the surveillance room
found the hearing aid.

07:58.040 --> 07:58.790
It was mistakenly thrown

07:58.790 --> 08:00.040
into the garbage bag during cleaning.

08:00.040 --> 08:02.390
Mr. Ji has already sent someone
to stop the garbage truck.

08:02.390 --> 08:03.800
Okay, I'll go take a look.

08:08.690 --> 08:10.360
Why did the garbage truck leave so fast?

08:10.360 --> 08:11.270
The garbage truck left?

08:11.270 --> 08:12.090
When did it leave?

08:12.090 --> 08:13.950
We just went out and saw it drive away.

08:13.950 --> 08:14.960
Okay, thank you.

08:33.960 --> 08:36.020
Sir, catch up with
that garbage truck ahead.

08:36.020 --> 08:36.679
Alright.

08:50.360 --> 08:51.050
It's raining.

08:51.050 --> 08:53.380
Should I keep following that truck, Miss?

08:53.400 --> 08:53.920
Yes.

08:54.790 --> 08:55.480
Alright.

09:30.160 --> 09:31.120
Sir.

09:31.400 --> 09:32.280
Wait a minute.

09:32.650 --> 09:35.500
Wait a minute. Sir.

09:35.530 --> 09:36.420
What's wrong?

09:36.440 --> 09:38.570
I am the lobby manager of Purong Hotel.

09:39.510 --> 09:40.960
We have a student
taking the college entrance exam.

09:40.960 --> 09:43.200
His hearing aid
ended up in the trash.

09:43.220 --> 09:45.520
Could you do me a favor
and let me look for it?

09:45.520 --> 09:47.650
Otherwise, it'll affect
the child's exam tomorrow.

09:47.650 --> 09:48.450
Thank you.

09:49.530 --> 09:51.320
Then I can only dump the garbage outside

09:51.320 --> 09:52.380
for you to search, is that okay?

09:52.380 --> 09:53.280
Yes, yes.

09:53.750 --> 09:56.010
Wang, dump the garbage behind the truck.

10:01.360 --> 10:02.030
Thank you.

10:03.150 --> 10:07.030
[Purong Hotel]

10:08.600 --> 10:09.360
Mr. Ji.

10:13.290 --> 10:14.600
Have the guests gone back?

10:14.600 --> 10:16.220
Ms. Xu has calmed the guests down.

10:16.220 --> 10:18.120
They are waiting in their room now.

10:18.120 --> 10:19.240
Where is she now?

10:19.290 --> 10:20.270
The garbage truck has already left.

10:20.270 --> 10:21.600
Ms. Xu has gone after it.

10:23.240 --> 10:24.000
It is raining so heavily.

10:24.000 --> 10:24.870
She went alone?

10:28.440 --> 10:29.040
Mr...

10:29.790 --> 10:31.000
The number you dialed

10:31.000 --> 10:32.060
cannot be reached.

10:32.470 --> 10:34.050
Please try again later.

10:49.440 --> 10:51.440
The black ones are from the kitchen.

10:53.880 --> 10:54.740
The red ones...

10:55.910 --> 10:58.240
The red ones are from the HSKP Department.

10:58.480 --> 10:59.150
The blue ones...

10:59.150 --> 11:00.810
The blue ones are from the gym.

11:04.870 --> 11:05.730
Blue ones.

11:25.370 --> 11:26.040
Blue ones.

11:26.160 --> 11:26.760
Blue ones.

11:37.400 --> 11:38.360
Found it!

11:39.360 --> 11:40.190
Found it!

11:46.000 --> 11:46.480
Okay.

11:52.540 --> 11:53.250
Sir.

11:53.780 --> 11:54.450
Thank you.

11:54.520 --> 11:55.880
I found it.

11:56.110 --> 11:57.130
Thank you so much.

11:58.240 --> 12:00.240
I made a mess of the garbage.

12:00.270 --> 12:01.670
Let me help you clean it up.

12:01.670 --> 12:02.360
No need.

12:02.400 --> 12:03.730
It's already very late.

12:03.800 --> 12:04.790
We will take care of it.

12:04.790 --> 12:06.930
Hurry back and give
the thing to the student.

12:06.930 --> 12:07.570
Thank you.

12:07.920 --> 12:08.740
It's nothing.

12:49.160 --> 12:50.000
Xu Miyu!

12:53.370 --> 12:54.550
I found it.

12:54.790 --> 12:57.200
I found the student's hearing aid.

12:57.060 --> 12:58.800
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

13:00.570 --> 13:02.210
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

13:01.920 --> 13:03.090
I found it!

13:04.430 --> 13:06.340
♪ People in the city ♪

13:07.160 --> 13:10.100
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

13:12.020 --> 13:13.100
Are you out of your mind?

13:12.030 --> 13:13.840
♪ The palms of time ♪

13:13.930 --> 13:15.740
Couldn't you ask someone else for help?

13:15.740 --> 13:18.880
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

13:15.920 --> 13:17.980
Can you take better care of yourself?

13:19.050 --> 13:20.910
Is that what you wanted to say to me?

13:19.490 --> 13:22.410
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

13:22.360 --> 13:22.740
You...

13:22.740 --> 13:24.160
My business is none of your concern!

13:23.410 --> 13:25.450
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

13:24.630 --> 13:25.650
It's raining!

13:26.930 --> 13:30.130
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

13:28.810 --> 13:29.510
Hey!

13:30.720 --> 13:33.750
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

13:34.340 --> 13:37.460
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

13:38.200 --> 13:40.680
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

13:42.240 --> 13:45.550
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

13:46.100 --> 13:49.470
♪ The forgotten past ♪

13:50.010 --> 13:52.390
♪ Walking through this world ♪

13:53.810 --> 13:58.860
[E-bike Parking Area]

13:54.450 --> 13:58.330
♪ Leaving no regrets behind ♪

13:58.810 --> 13:59.630
Excuse me.

13:58.930 --> 14:00.590
[Fever Clinic]

14:00.840 --> 14:01.520
Nurse.

14:01.630 --> 14:02.200
What's wrong?

14:02.200 --> 14:03.000
She has a fever and fainted.

14:03.000 --> 14:03.630
Let's find a bed first.

14:03.630 --> 14:04.960
You can register later.

14:16.690 --> 14:17.430
What medicine is this?

14:17.430 --> 14:18.790
Why is she in so much pain?

14:18.790 --> 14:19.750
Azithromycin.

14:19.820 --> 14:21.020
It's antibacterial.

14:21.080 --> 14:23.880
It hurts a bit when it
irritates the blood vessels.

14:26.190 --> 14:27.930
Is there any way to relieve it?

14:29.360 --> 14:31.360
I've already slowed down the speed.

14:31.480 --> 14:33.480
As her family, here's what you can do.

14:33.480 --> 14:34.740
Rub it for the patient.

14:34.790 --> 14:36.230
She will feel better.

14:36.670 --> 14:37.120
Okay.

14:42.220 --> 14:43.060
Yes.

14:43.480 --> 14:44.340
Just like that.

14:44.510 --> 14:46.270
Remember to call us when the IV runs out.

14:46.270 --> 14:46.870
Thank you.

15:04.890 --> 15:07.190
♪ I know at the start of every story ♪

15:07.960 --> 15:10.050
♪ They all feel somewhat the same ♪

15:11.940 --> 15:14.140
♪ Just never thought I would ♪

15:15.170 --> 15:17.080
♪ Fall for you so deeply ♪

15:18.900 --> 15:21.220
♪ Why did I have to lose myself? ♪

15:21.740 --> 15:23.970
♪ In the virtual world ♪

15:25.240 --> 15:30.760
♪ Unfinished dreams hurt the most ♪

15:32.180 --> 15:34.100
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

15:34.580 --> 15:37.960
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

15:39.470 --> 15:41.060
♪ Until I met you ♪

15:41.860 --> 15:44.960
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

15:45.540 --> 15:47.500
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

15:47.960 --> 15:49.690
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

15:50.150 --> 15:51.450
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

15:51.770 --> 15:53.620
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

15:54.030 --> 15:57.030
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

15:57.250 --> 15:58.910
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

15:59.810 --> 16:01.590
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

16:01.800 --> 16:03.490
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

16:04.270 --> 16:06.470
♪ Love really hurts ♪

16:04.870 --> 16:06.200
Are you out of your mind?

16:06.900 --> 16:08.400
Couldn't you ask someone else for help?

16:07.700 --> 16:12.360
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

16:08.700 --> 16:10.760
Can you take better care of yourself?

16:12.200 --> 16:14.130
Is that what you wanted to say to me?

16:15.080 --> 16:15.560
You...

16:15.680 --> 16:17.680
My business is none of your concern!

16:18.050 --> 16:19.150
It's raining!

16:19.480 --> 16:22.140
You'll get sick if you
stay in the rain like this!

16:25.000 --> 16:26.970
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

16:27.300 --> 16:30.660
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

16:32.290 --> 16:33.910
♪ Until I met you ♪

16:34.680 --> 16:38.090
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

16:38.510 --> 16:40.480
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

16:40.820 --> 16:42.610
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

16:42.990 --> 16:44.250
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

16:44.600 --> 16:46.410
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

16:46.780 --> 16:49.800
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

16:50.130 --> 16:51.650
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

16:52.750 --> 16:54.330
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

16:54.610 --> 16:56.340
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

16:57.200 --> 16:59.330
♪ Love really hurts ♪

17:00.360 --> 17:05.030
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

17:08.520 --> 17:11.240
♪ Only when you've been hurt by love
do you realize how crazy you once were ♪

17:11.740 --> 17:14.660
♪ A beautiful dream
turns into a nightmare in an instant ♪

17:15.910 --> 17:20.800
♪ You are a neon light
I could never catch ♪

17:21.770 --> 17:23.690
♪ I loved you recklessly ♪

17:25.069 --> 17:27.440
♪ And ended up covered in wounds ♪

17:28.510 --> 17:29.800
♪ Yet I still believe in ♪

17:30.810 --> 17:33.360
♪ The sky after the rain ♪

17:35.220 --> 17:36.960
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

17:37.600 --> 17:39.110
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

17:40.090 --> 17:41.760
♪ Love really hurts ♪

17:43.300 --> 17:47.680
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

17:47.780 --> 17:48.600
You're awake.

17:50.550 --> 17:58.480
♪ In the end, everything came to nothing ♪

17:52.960 --> 17:53.520
Miyu.

17:53.930 --> 17:54.970
Qiaoqi?

17:56.470 --> 17:57.430
Why are you here?

17:57.450 --> 17:59.840
You ask me? I wanted to ask you.

17:59.860 --> 18:00.750
How did you get

18:00.750 --> 18:02.650
acute pneumonia just from working?

18:02.650 --> 18:03.960
If Mr. Ji hadn't called me,

18:03.960 --> 18:06.560
I wouldn't have known
you were in the hospital.

18:06.930 --> 18:08.030
The hearing aid.

18:08.380 --> 18:09.820
Lie down. Don't move.

18:11.300 --> 18:12.760
I knew you'd ask this.

18:12.890 --> 18:14.350
Mr. Ji already had someone

18:14.350 --> 18:17.000
send the hearing aid back to the hotel
for the student last night.

18:17.000 --> 18:18.330
He told you not to worry.

18:21.890 --> 18:22.750
What about him?

18:22.880 --> 18:26.480
He said there was something going on
at the hotel, so he went back.

18:28.270 --> 18:29.870
What's going on with you two?

18:30.310 --> 18:31.110
Did you fight?

18:32.200 --> 18:34.200
He looked pretty worried about you.

18:35.550 --> 18:37.280
Don't bother with him anymore.

18:39.240 --> 18:40.040
Get some rest.

18:53.130 --> 18:53.650
Come in.

18:55.680 --> 18:56.400
Mr. Xue,

18:56.630 --> 18:57.830
Mr. Qian from the sales department

18:57.830 --> 18:59.900
and Mr. Huang from the finance department
keep asking

18:59.900 --> 19:02.030
if the project progress report meeting
later is still on.

19:02.030 --> 19:03.550
Yes, what's wrong?

19:03.590 --> 19:05.160
They said Mr. Ji isn't here,

19:05.240 --> 19:06.310
so there's no one to host it.

19:06.310 --> 19:07.510
Who said I'm not here?

19:08.350 --> 19:09.000
Mr. Ji.

19:09.900 --> 19:12.230
I will inform the directors immediately.

19:18.640 --> 19:20.480
Didn't I tell you to go home and rest?

19:20.480 --> 19:22.140
Why did you come to work again?

19:22.790 --> 19:24.220
You look exhausted.

19:25.000 --> 19:25.720
Rui.

19:26.350 --> 19:27.550
I want a cup of coffee.

19:43.170 --> 19:45.100
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

19:55.640 --> 19:57.590
Why are you looking at your phone again?

19:57.590 --> 19:58.830
Didn't you already use my phone

19:58.830 --> 20:00.370
to call your mom?

20:03.510 --> 20:04.770
It's not to call my mom.

20:05.030 --> 20:06.440
I need to check the work group chats.

20:06.440 --> 20:08.430
I haven't checked them since last night.

20:08.430 --> 20:09.720
I'm afraid someone is looking for me.

20:09.720 --> 20:10.810
I knew it.

20:11.680 --> 20:13.140
Don't even think about it.

20:13.340 --> 20:14.850
I already asked for leave for you today.

20:14.850 --> 20:16.610
You are not allowed to work today.

20:16.610 --> 20:18.320
But the college entrance examination
isn't over yet.

20:18.320 --> 20:19.380
I'm afraid that...

20:20.440 --> 20:21.400
Without you, Purong

20:21.400 --> 20:23.120
will still run.

20:23.590 --> 20:25.880
Today, you just need to rest and recover.

20:26.070 --> 20:27.000
No more overworking.

20:27.000 --> 20:27.800
Do you hear me?

20:33.780 --> 20:35.310
I'll put the hot water and the medicine

20:35.310 --> 20:36.390
here for you.

20:36.480 --> 20:37.670
Remember to take it.

20:38.160 --> 20:38.890
I'm leaving.

20:39.880 --> 20:40.970
Ride safe.

20:55.790 --> 20:56.390
Chef Jiao.

20:58.190 --> 21:00.120
This is prepared for the guests.

21:00.660 --> 21:02.380
What guests?

21:02.400 --> 21:04.930
Are the guests more important
or my daughter?

21:05.370 --> 21:06.550
When you have your own kids,

21:06.550 --> 21:08.540
you'll understand.

21:11.790 --> 21:12.400
But I...

21:21.550 --> 21:23.080
Chef Jiao, you can't leave.

21:23.140 --> 21:25.000
Dinner hasn't been prepared yet.

21:26.070 --> 21:27.240
Didn't you keep asking me

21:27.240 --> 21:29.440
when you could try your hand at it?

21:30.880 --> 21:31.590
Yes.

21:31.590 --> 21:32.350
When?

21:32.720 --> 21:33.510
Right now.

21:39.350 --> 21:41.480
Chef Jiao! Chef Jiao!

21:42.720 --> 21:44.000
This young man.

21:44.840 --> 21:47.450
Thinking he can stop me.

21:48.510 --> 21:49.920
-I’m sorry.
-I’m sorry.

21:50.720 --> 21:51.440
Mr. Tan.

21:51.440 --> 21:52.270
Mrs. Xu.

21:52.290 --> 21:53.030
Sorry.

21:53.550 --> 21:54.700
Did the oil get on you?

21:54.700 --> 21:55.440
No, no.

21:55.440 --> 21:55.920
Really.

21:55.920 --> 21:56.920
How about you give me your clothes

21:56.920 --> 21:58.030
and I'll dry-clean them for you?

21:58.030 --> 21:59.230
I'll have my daughter

21:59.240 --> 22:01.640
-bring them to your room later.
-It's okay.

22:02.020 --> 22:04.090
By the way, how is Miyu doing?

22:05.350 --> 22:06.650
I heard she's sick.

22:07.640 --> 22:08.470
Yes, yes.

22:08.500 --> 22:10.530
You see, I'm bringing her food.

22:10.750 --> 22:11.680
Is it serious?

22:13.810 --> 22:15.000
How should I put it?

22:15.550 --> 22:17.280
It's on and off.

22:17.590 --> 22:19.070
I'm so worried.

22:19.900 --> 22:22.530
Why don't you come with me to see her?

22:22.810 --> 22:24.240
If Miyu knows you're visiting her,

22:24.240 --> 22:25.340
she will be very happy.

22:25.340 --> 22:27.860
Then she'll recover once she's happy.

22:28.070 --> 22:28.680
Well...

22:29.070 --> 22:29.790
Is that okay?

22:29.790 --> 22:30.730
Yes, it is.

22:30.880 --> 22:31.600
Of course.

22:31.960 --> 22:32.270
Xia,

22:32.310 --> 22:32.910
come here.

22:33.240 --> 22:34.940
Could you take it to storage?

22:34.970 --> 22:36.400
-It’s Mr. Tan's.
-Please take it to storage for me.

22:36.400 --> 22:37.460
-Okay.
-Thank you.

22:37.590 --> 22:38.160
I'll take you there.

22:38.160 --> 22:38.960
Okay.

22:38.960 --> 22:39.400
Let's go together.

22:39.400 --> 22:40.310
I got this.

22:40.310 --> 22:40.640
You take it.

22:40.640 --> 22:41.240
I got this.

22:54.030 --> 22:54.780
Miyu.

22:54.980 --> 22:56.110
I'm baking cookies.

22:56.270 --> 22:57.470
They'll be done soon.

23:00.680 --> 23:02.600
Go clean up.

23:03.520 --> 23:04.520
I just cleaned up.

23:04.530 --> 23:06.650
I mean you.

23:06.680 --> 23:08.030
Look at what you're wearing.

23:08.030 --> 23:09.030
Even a sack

23:09.050 --> 23:10.400
looks better than that.

23:10.510 --> 23:11.530
Go change your clothes.

23:11.530 --> 23:12.640
Change into that Chanel-style outfit.

23:12.640 --> 23:13.860
Go, go.

23:13.890 --> 23:15.110
Why?

23:15.400 --> 23:17.200
You have a visitor.

23:17.200 --> 23:18.830
A visitor? Who?

23:18.910 --> 23:19.970
Miyu, it's me.

23:20.000 --> 23:21.230
May I come in?

23:21.890 --> 23:23.610
Mr. Tan is here to see you.

23:23.770 --> 23:25.810
He's such a gentleman.

23:25.870 --> 23:26.920
When he arrived at the door,

23:26.920 --> 23:28.980
he insisted I come in and let you know.

23:29.200 --> 23:30.600
He knows his boundaries.

23:30.760 --> 23:32.140
Where are yours?

23:32.170 --> 23:32.590
I...

23:32.830 --> 23:34.690
I'll talk to you about this later.

23:36.030 --> 23:37.850
Put on some lipstick.

23:38.330 --> 23:39.090
Enough.

23:42.680 --> 23:44.070
Mr. Tan, please come in.

23:44.660 --> 23:45.990
Are you feeling better?

23:46.440 --> 23:47.770
Much better, thank you.

23:48.240 --> 23:48.770
Is it okay?

23:48.770 --> 23:50.230
Yes, come in.

23:51.440 --> 23:52.030
Well,

23:52.560 --> 23:53.930
the hotel wants me back.

23:54.400 --> 23:55.110
Well,

23:55.140 --> 23:56.620
isn't there

23:56.650 --> 23:57.950
a performance tonight?

23:57.950 --> 23:59.090
I'm leaving now.

23:59.110 --> 24:00.630
Take your time.

24:00.680 --> 24:01.030
Okay.

24:01.030 --> 24:01.680
You two take your time talking.

24:01.680 --> 24:02.290
Careful, slow down.

24:02.290 --> 24:02.680
Okay.

24:03.440 --> 24:04.290
I am heading back now.

24:04.290 --> 24:06.020
Take your time, take your time.

24:06.880 --> 24:07.350
Mom.

24:16.440 --> 24:17.970
Mr. Tan, please have a seat.

24:19.000 --> 24:19.590
Okay.

24:32.790 --> 24:33.460
Chef Jiao,

24:33.980 --> 24:35.240
why are you back again?

24:36.300 --> 24:37.440
Your hedgehog

24:38.590 --> 24:40.640
looks like a mouse.

24:41.450 --> 24:43.050
You didn't use enough flour.

24:43.270 --> 24:44.070
Let me tell you,

24:44.070 --> 24:45.260
you won't be able
to cut out the spines later.

24:45.260 --> 24:46.660
Here, watch me.

24:46.960 --> 24:48.160
You kids.

24:48.160 --> 24:49.890
You really can't do without me.

24:50.830 --> 24:51.370
Look.

24:52.310 --> 24:53.770
Isn't this Miyu's dinner?

25:00.160 --> 25:01.160
Come on, look.

25:10.890 --> 25:12.750
You stayed at the airport all day?

25:14.110 --> 25:14.900
It's thunderstorm season.

25:14.900 --> 25:16.430
Many flights are grounded.

25:16.680 --> 25:18.080
It's okay. I'm used to it.

25:18.490 --> 25:20.350
Then you must not have eaten well.

25:20.480 --> 25:21.880
The noodles will be ready soon.

25:21.880 --> 25:22.680
Okay, no rush.

25:23.920 --> 25:25.310
Have some cookies first.

25:25.310 --> 25:25.880
Okay.

25:31.680 --> 25:32.510
Okay, I got it.

25:32.530 --> 25:33.950
I'll come back soon.

25:34.880 --> 25:35.480
Tomorrow?

25:35.690 --> 25:37.940
I'm not sure. I can't promise.

25:40.670 --> 25:41.750
Okay, bye.

25:47.000 --> 25:48.060
-Here.
-Thank you.

25:49.720 --> 25:50.940
You must be busy with work.

25:50.940 --> 25:51.490
No.

25:56.840 --> 25:58.720
You've been to the Getty Museum too?

25:58.720 --> 25:59.270
Yeah.

25:59.440 --> 26:01.430
The Getty Center or the Getty Villa?

26:01.430 --> 26:02.430
The Getty Center.

26:02.880 --> 26:04.830
I just wanted to see for myself

26:04.830 --> 26:07.260
how amazing those masterpieces

26:07.680 --> 26:09.940
you usually only see in books really are.

26:10.270 --> 26:11.310
Then...

26:11.310 --> 26:12.110
How was it?

26:12.240 --> 26:14.350
I was actually blown away

26:14.350 --> 26:15.680
by Paul Getty's wealth.

26:16.590 --> 26:18.520
Degas' dancers,

26:18.590 --> 26:19.930
Van Gogh's Irises,

26:20.070 --> 26:21.030
Munch's The Scream,

26:21.030 --> 26:22.030
Monet's Water Lilies,

26:22.030 --> 26:23.270
and those portraits of Louis XIV

26:23.270 --> 26:24.960
covered in gold and silver,

26:25.200 --> 26:26.590
all effortlessly embraced

26:26.590 --> 26:28.070
by this museum.

26:28.790 --> 26:31.510
Inside lies an elegant,
understated world of art.

26:31.510 --> 26:34.960
Outside unfolds a tropical, ocean breeze
filled with birdsong and blooming flowers.

26:34.960 --> 26:36.920
It's simply the heaven I imagined.

26:41.920 --> 26:42.590
I'm sorry.

26:43.110 --> 26:44.680
I got a bit carried away
in front of an expert.

26:44.680 --> 26:45.640
No. No.

26:45.880 --> 26:47.180
What you said
is exactly what I was thinking.

26:47.180 --> 26:48.450
I was just surprised

26:48.470 --> 26:50.550
at how much you know about Western art.

26:50.550 --> 26:51.920
Not that much.

26:52.070 --> 26:53.830
When I was in college,

26:53.920 --> 26:55.160
I thought I might work

26:55.160 --> 26:57.030
in a hotel-related
profession in the future

26:57.030 --> 26:58.200
and might need this knowledge.

26:58.200 --> 27:00.440
So I read some books on art,

27:00.440 --> 27:02.200
and the more I read,
the more fascinated I became.

27:02.200 --> 27:03.440
I just liked it,

27:03.920 --> 27:05.730
so I learned a bit about it.

27:06.160 --> 27:07.750
That's not just a bit.

27:10.160 --> 27:10.790
The pot.

27:10.890 --> 27:12.820
It's okay, let me do it. Have a seat.

27:55.440 --> 27:56.270
Thanks.

27:57.160 --> 27:58.020
Smells so good.

28:02.090 --> 28:02.800
Your phone.

28:05.400 --> 28:06.500
It's not important.

28:06.500 --> 28:08.950
You skipped work to come here, didn't you?

28:12.160 --> 28:13.480
I know you must be worried

28:13.480 --> 28:15.510
about the old Mr. Tan's health, right?

28:15.510 --> 28:17.660
He has been experiencing
chest tightness lately,

28:17.660 --> 28:19.260
but everything else is fine.

28:19.350 --> 28:20.110
Don't worry.

28:20.160 --> 28:21.750
Even though I left the HSKP Department,

28:21.750 --> 28:23.720
I'm still in touch with the girls

28:23.720 --> 28:25.050
on the executive floor.

28:26.070 --> 28:27.530
If you are really worried,

28:27.550 --> 28:28.880
you can add me on WeChat.

28:28.960 --> 28:31.000
Then next time you're worried,

28:31.000 --> 28:32.060
you can just ask me.

28:32.150 --> 28:32.740
Okay.

28:33.400 --> 28:34.400
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

29:00.920 --> 29:03.740
[Li Qiaoqi]

29:07.050 --> 29:08.100
Hello, Mr. Ji.

29:09.110 --> 29:09.940
Qiaoqi.

29:10.440 --> 29:11.330
Miyu, she...

29:11.830 --> 29:12.350
Mr. Ji.

29:12.910 --> 29:15.310
I don't know what
happened between you two.

29:15.600 --> 29:16.670
But regarding Miyu,

29:16.670 --> 29:18.400
if she doesn't want you to know,

29:18.480 --> 29:19.680
I can't tell you.

29:19.920 --> 29:20.480
Sorry.

29:20.970 --> 29:22.640
Okay, I know.

29:23.090 --> 29:23.810
Mr. Ji,

29:24.240 --> 29:25.160
for last night,

29:25.160 --> 29:26.960
I want to thank you on behalf of Miyu.

29:26.960 --> 29:28.620
The doctor said the IV worked very well.

29:28.620 --> 29:30.620
She just needs to rest for a few days.

29:31.760 --> 29:32.360
Thank you.

29:39.770 --> 29:40.430
Still here?

29:42.310 --> 29:42.940
By the way,

29:43.590 --> 29:45.260
there's an industry exhibition
this weekend,

29:45.260 --> 29:46.620
and we've been invited.

29:47.830 --> 29:49.090
They gave us 2 tickets.

29:49.790 --> 29:51.450
Should I clear your schedule?

29:54.480 --> 29:56.550
[The 15th
Shanghai International Hospitality Expo]

30:00.000 --> 30:03.040
Would you rather I come with you,

30:03.070 --> 30:05.400
or have Ms. Xu join you?

30:08.730 --> 30:10.690
I'll let you know tomorrow.

30:11.880 --> 30:12.310
Okay.

30:16.090 --> 30:20.110
[The 15th
Shanghai International Hospitality Expo]

30:24.720 --> 30:25.770
You're right.

30:27.180 --> 30:29.710
Then do you know
about the Shanghai Biennale?

30:30.460 --> 30:34.270
It's at the Shanghai Museum
of Contemporary Art.

30:34.590 --> 30:37.160
I remember their theme in 2023 was...

30:37.160 --> 30:38.160
"Cosmos Cinema".

30:40.400 --> 30:42.070
At that time, they had a concept called

30:42.070 --> 30:44.270
"All beings are equal under the stars".

30:44.550 --> 30:47.110
I thought that concept
was absolutely stunning.

30:47.110 --> 30:48.510
You really know
Shanghai's contemporary art

30:48.510 --> 30:49.920
like the back of your hand.

30:49.920 --> 30:52.520
Of course. I used to
love going to exhibitions.

30:52.640 --> 30:55.100
Are you familiar
with the scene in Hong Kong?

30:55.160 --> 30:55.830
Unfortunately,

30:55.830 --> 30:58.110
I'm always in a hurry
every time I go to Hong Kong.

30:58.110 --> 30:59.640
Actually, I've always wanted to visit

30:59.640 --> 31:00.720
the M+ Museum

31:00.720 --> 31:02.820
and the Asia Art Archive.

31:03.030 --> 31:04.160
This weekend,

31:04.240 --> 31:05.700
there is an exhibition at M+.

31:05.700 --> 31:07.360
Would you like to go together?

31:08.470 --> 31:09.550
The round trip takes only 2 days,

31:09.550 --> 31:11.150
so it won't affect your work.

31:12.310 --> 31:14.240
I have to work shifts this weekend.

31:16.600 --> 31:18.320
Miyu, there is something

31:19.160 --> 31:21.360
that might be a bit presumptuous to say.

31:21.920 --> 31:23.450
You were so happy just now,

31:23.490 --> 31:24.510
talking about this.

31:24.510 --> 31:26.570
You probably didn't even realize it.

31:26.980 --> 31:30.390
And you were very charming, really.

31:32.110 --> 31:33.200
When I got here, your mom told me

31:33.200 --> 31:35.400
that you were in a bad mood. Is that true?

31:36.110 --> 31:37.930
Then why not treat this trip

31:38.200 --> 31:39.700
as a way to clear your mind?

31:39.860 --> 31:40.960
Maybe after you come back,

31:40.960 --> 31:42.420
you'll feel differently.

31:45.960 --> 31:47.690
No need to answer me right away.

31:48.070 --> 31:48.930
Think about it.

31:50.750 --> 31:51.940
Thank you, Mr. Tan.

31:54.390 --> 31:55.930
I'll get going now.

31:57.350 --> 31:58.160
See you tomorrow.

31:58.160 --> 31:59.160
See you tomorrow.

32:55.010 --> 32:56.610
[Welcome to Purong Hotel]

32:57.630 --> 32:58.430
Good morning.

32:58.510 --> 32:59.720
Good morning, Ms. Xu.

33:01.720 --> 33:02.610
Ms. Xu.

33:03.550 --> 33:04.270
Ms. Xu.

33:05.030 --> 33:06.140
I heard you were sick.

33:06.140 --> 33:07.800
So I bought some supplements.

33:08.030 --> 33:09.890
I didn't know you'd be at work today.

33:09.890 --> 33:11.290
They are still in my room.

33:11.510 --> 33:12.900
I'll bring them to you later.

33:12.900 --> 33:13.790
I'm alright.

33:14.000 --> 33:16.000
We cannot accept gifts from guests.

33:16.180 --> 33:17.720
As long as Yuze's exam wasn't affected.

33:17.720 --> 33:18.730
The exam went smoothly.

33:18.730 --> 33:19.670
Thank you, Miss.

33:19.690 --> 33:20.510
That's great.

33:21.400 --> 33:23.000
Today is the last day, right?

33:23.070 --> 33:23.920
You should hurry.

33:23.920 --> 33:24.740
Don't be late.

33:24.610 --> 33:29.520
[Purong Hotel]

33:24.790 --> 33:25.920
Okay, we'll get going now.

33:25.920 --> 33:27.070
Good luck on the exam.

33:27.070 --> 33:28.600
Thank you, Ms. Xu. Goodbye.

33:28.830 --> 33:29.430
Take care.

33:36.600 --> 33:37.800
Good morning, Mr. Ji.

33:37.880 --> 33:38.680
Good morning.

33:40.090 --> 33:41.430
Are you feeling better?

33:41.460 --> 33:42.630
I'm fully recovered.

33:42.630 --> 33:43.630
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

33:46.610 --> 33:49.110
There is an industry expo this weekend

33:49.130 --> 33:51.460
at Pudong New International Expo Centre.

33:52.160 --> 33:53.290
Want to go together?

34:01.330 --> 34:02.270
Mr. Tan.

34:09.949 --> 34:11.550
I've got plans this weekend.

34:11.560 --> 34:12.560
You've got plans?

34:13.170 --> 34:14.170
I'm sorry, Mr. Ji.

34:14.409 --> 34:15.610
I'll get back to work.

34:24.110 --> 34:24.389
[Monday, June 9]

34:29.530 --> 34:31.790
[Miyu]

34:32.760 --> 34:34.670
Mr. Tan, let's go together.

34:45.969 --> 34:46.780
Okay.

34:46.500 --> 34:46.860
[Tan Jizhou]

34:55.290 --> 34:56.550
Sometimes,

34:57.000 --> 34:58.240
accepting an invitation

34:58.070 --> 34:59.980
♪ Life is full of ♪

34:58.270 --> 34:59.600
doesn't mean anything.

35:00.140 --> 35:01.800
But rejecting someone's invitation

35:01.030 --> 35:03.680
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

35:02.160 --> 35:04.290
is because you have
feelings for them.

35:05.210 --> 35:09.060
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

35:05.830 --> 35:07.130
What am I afraid of?

35:10.650 --> 35:12.650
♪ All those confusions ♪

35:13.240 --> 35:16.960
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

35:17.840 --> 35:21.840
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

35:25.240 --> 35:27.360
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

35:28.770 --> 35:30.690
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

35:32.520 --> 35:36.230
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

35:38.040 --> 35:39.840
♪ Busy and restless ♪

35:40.440 --> 35:43.870
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

35:45.220 --> 35:49.280
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

35:51.160 --> 35:53.510
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

35:54.840 --> 35:56.870
♪ Don't look back ♪

35:57.840 --> 35:59.610
♪ I've already learned ♪

36:00.390 --> 36:04.220
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

36:04.920 --> 36:06.580
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

36:07.380 --> 36:11.310
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

36:12.300 --> 36:15.240
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

36:15.940 --> 36:18.550
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

36:19.160 --> 36:20.870
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

36:23.190 --> 36:24.360
Is there a problem?

36:28.690 --> 36:32.490
[Hong Kong, China]

36:30.000 --> 36:31.030
Take care.

36:34.400 --> 36:35.320
Good evening, Mr. Tan.

36:35.320 --> 36:35.760
Hello.

36:35.760 --> 36:37.160
How can I help you?

36:37.190 --> 36:38.030
I booked

36:38.070 --> 36:39.730
an Executive 80 Sea View Room.

36:40.170 --> 36:40.810
Okay.

36:42.550 --> 36:44.340
I'll just take a standard room.

36:45.570 --> 36:46.570
Wait a moment.

36:47.630 --> 36:48.550
It's fine.

36:48.550 --> 36:50.980
This hotel has a partnership
with our company.

36:50.980 --> 36:52.210
I came here on my own.

36:52.360 --> 36:53.620
How could I let you pay?

36:55.740 --> 36:56.960
Alright, it's up to you.

36:56.960 --> 36:58.890
Excuse me, a standard room please.

37:00.410 --> 37:01.760
Your room has been booked.

37:01.760 --> 37:02.760
Have a good night.

37:02.960 --> 37:04.020
Let's go. This way.

37:05.150 --> 37:05.800
By the way,

37:05.820 --> 37:08.440
don't forget to accept
the money I transferred for the flight.

37:08.440 --> 37:09.550
I dragged you to this exhibition.

37:09.550 --> 37:10.960
I'm already very happy
that you could come.

37:10.960 --> 37:12.760
Let's not talk about this, okay?

37:12.760 --> 37:14.070
I'm the happy one.

37:14.070 --> 37:15.400
You helped me fulfill this dream

37:15.400 --> 37:16.930
and left me with no regrets.

37:18.230 --> 37:18.630
Okay.

37:19.240 --> 37:21.440
Then I'll pick you up
at 10:00 a.m. tomorrow.

37:21.440 --> 37:22.970
Remember to eat breakfast.

37:26.190 --> 37:26.880
See you tomorrow.

37:26.880 --> 37:27.880
See you tomorrow.

39:03.080 --> 39:07.750
[Central]

39:06.190 --> 39:08.650
So do you still have
any regrets after today?

39:08.880 --> 39:09.630
Today,

39:09.670 --> 39:12.360
we even caught the debut
of that mysterious pearl piece

39:12.360 --> 39:13.880
from the British royal family today.

39:13.880 --> 39:15.210
We were really so lucky.

39:15.960 --> 39:18.670
[Hans Bookstore]

39:16.880 --> 39:18.320
So you like pearls.

39:18.880 --> 39:21.150
I think pearls emit

39:21.150 --> 39:22.960
an elegant and pure glow.

39:24.360 --> 39:25.280
Just like you.

39:37.480 --> 39:38.610
Want to grab a drink?

39:42.580 --> 39:46.540
[Moden Alley]

39:56.210 --> 39:56.890
Rui.

39:57.340 --> 39:59.340
I asked you to invite
Xu Miyu to the exhibition,

39:59.340 --> 40:01.270
and she ended up going to Hong Kong?

40:03.190 --> 40:04.460
She decided it herself.

40:04.460 --> 40:05.530
I had no say in it.

40:06.180 --> 40:08.780
Do you not want to know
why she went to Hong Kong?

40:10.710 --> 40:12.440
Please do not tell me, alright?

40:12.590 --> 40:13.630
Oh, you.

40:14.190 --> 40:16.490
They are almost together.

40:16.930 --> 40:18.310
Are you going to give up?

40:19.070 --> 40:19.840
Rui,

40:20.600 --> 40:23.130
how long has it been
since you came to the Bund?

40:23.800 --> 40:24.630
How come there are so many

40:24.630 --> 40:25.630
new buildings?

40:26.400 --> 40:27.670
I don't think I've seen them before.
